data.description: Step into a truly exceptional lakeside home that offers an unmatched blend of natural beauty and modern comforts. This delightful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is perfectly situated just a stone's throw from the tranquil East Lake, making it the ideal retreat for those seeking both serenity and sophistication. You will find a well designed floor plan that seamlessly connects the living area, dining space, kitchen and office. Convenience is key, and you'll find it in the attached garage, providing space for your vehicle. Beyond the garage lies a charming barn that offers three distinct spaces, eagerly awaiting your personal touch. Whether you envision a creative craft room, a recreational haven (complete with a pool table and a projector/speaker system that stay with the property), or your very own man cave, the possibilities are limited only by your imagination.  Yet, most sought after aspect of this property is undoubtedly the private East lake frontage just a short stroll away. Newly constructed steps beckon you down to this aquatic haven, where the serene waters of East Lake await your enjoyment. This lakeside area has been thoughtfully designed as a fantastic outdoor entertaining space, and all the lakeside furniture remains, ensuring you can relish in the spectacular views and host gatherings with ease.
